### Source Code from particle.io

```C 
int rainPin = A0;

void setup() {
    
  pinMode(rainPin, INPUT);

}

void loop() {
 // read the input on analog pin 0:
  int sensorValue = analogRead(rainPin);
  Particle.publish("YL-69", String(sensorValue), PRIVATE);
  delay(60000);

}
```
   
